# VedaAI Codebase Map (surgical-change guide)

**Phase:** 6 — Backend hardening (middleware largely done). Phase 5 frontend DONE.
**Tests:** shared 30 · api 71 · web 77 = **178** (must stay green).
**Truth order:** code/tests > git > `graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md` > docs.

## Monorepo layout

| Package | Role |
|---------|------|
| `packages/shared` | **Frozen contracts** — Zod schemas; types = `z.infer`. Never duplicate types elsewhere. |
| `apps/api` | Express API + BullMQ worker (`ENTRY=api` \| `worker` on Railway) |
| `apps/web` | Next.js 16 App Router, Redux Toolkit, Socket.IO client |

## Generation pipeline (touch carefully)

```
AssignmentForm → POST /api/assignments
  → assignment.service.create → repo.create + queue.enqueue
  → worker: buildPrompt → llm.complete (gemini) → parsePaper (+ repair)
  → repo.setDone → QueueEvents → Socket.IO (assignment:done|failed)
  → AssignmentOutputClient / QuestionPaperView
```

**Key files (backend):**
- `apps/api/src/server.ts` — API entry: Mongo, Redis, queue, Socket.IO, `createApp`
- `apps/api/src/worker.ts` — Worker entry + `createGenerateProcessor`
- `apps/api/src/services/assignment.service.ts` — create/list/find/delete
- `apps/api/src/adapters/db/assignment.repository.ts` — Mongo persistence
- `apps/api/src/domain/prompt.ts`, `parse.ts` — prompt + Zod validation/repair
- `apps/api/src/adapters/llm/providers/gemini.ts` — `GEMINI_MODEL` env (default gemini-3.1-flash-lite)
- `apps/api/src/lib/queue.ts`, `socket.ts` — BullMQ + realtime events

**Key files (frontend):**
- `apps/web/src/components/AssignmentForm.tsx` — create form + upload
- `apps/web/src/lib/useAssignmentSocket.ts` — generation status socket
- `apps/web/src/lib/useCloudinaryUpload.ts` — signed upload (URL only to API)
- `apps/web/src/components/AssignmentOutputClient.tsx`, `QuestionPaperView.tsx`
- `apps/web/src/store/slices/*` — form, assignments list, generation state

## Layering rule (every API change)

`route` → `service` → `domain` → Zod (`@vedaai/shared`) → `adapter` (db/llm/cache/storage).

Middleware stack on assignment routes: `validateBody` → `sanitize` → handler → `validateOutput`.
App-wide: `securityHeaders`, `rateLimitMiddleware`, `asyncHandler`, central `errorHandler`.

## Shared schemas (`packages/shared/src/schemas/`)

- `assignment.ts` — `AssignmentInput`, `AssignmentSummary`, status enum
- `question-paper.ts` — `QuestionPaper` (sections, questions, difficulty, marks)
- `socket.ts` — `assignment:queued|processing|done|failed` event payloads

## Routes (web)

- `/assignments` — list (`AssignmentsList`)
- `/assignments/create` — form (`AssignmentForm`)
- `/assignments/[id]` — output (`AssignmentOutputClient`); mobile hides bottom tab bar

Nav: `Sidebar` (desktop 304px), `MobileHeader`, `BottomTabBar`.

## DB (DEC-0004)

Normalized: `assignments` + `question_papers` + `questions` collections. Models in `apps/api/src/models/`.

## Infra (live)

- Web: https://vedaai-assessment-creator-two.vercel.app (`apps/web`)
- API: Railway `api` service; worker separate (`ENTRY=worker`)
- Redis: job queue + cache target (Phase 6 M3+)
- Uploads: Cloudinary signed from frontend; backend stores URL only

## Safe vs risky edits

| Safer (localized) | Higher blast radius |
|--------------------|---------------------|
| Single component styling/copy (`content/copy.json`) | `packages/shared` schema changes |
| `DifficultyBadge`, nav shell, PDF export | `assignment.repository`, worker processor |
| Middleware tuning in `apps/api/src/middleware/` | Socket event names/payloads |
| `domain/prompt.ts` wording | `createApp` middleware order |

